codex
The native D17a result is now characterized, not inferred: after stream stop, `GPS_RAW_INT` fell to no-fix at +1.019 s, absolute position was lost at +4.212 s, and Rover’s armed GUIDED mode changed itself to HOLD with `EKF failsafe` at +5.071 s. Steering/throttle outputs stayed neutral. I’m running the companion-HOLD candidate separately at +1.5 s so it is tested before Rover’s native action rather than being an idempotent command afterward.
